Bring water to a boil. Pour over tea bag, cinnamon stick and cloves in a teapot; cover and steep 5 minutes. Remove tea bag, squeezing gently. Stir SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, orange juice and lemon juice into tea. Pour tea through a wire-mesh strainer into cups, discarding spices. To make 4 servings: Bring 4 cups water to a boil. Pour over 3 regular-size tea bags, 2 cinnamon sticks, and 1/2 teaspoon whole cloves in a teapot; cover and steep 5 minutes. Remove tea bags, squeezing gently. Stir 12 packets SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, 1/4 cup orange juice and 1 1/2 teaspoons fresh lemon juice into tea. Pour tea through a wire-mesh strainer into cups, discarding spices.